The job is a quite bit difficult. In this cool action game for kids, you have to throw darts at the targets to score big. The only way to make extra points is to hit closer to the center without hurting the poor fellow. In this creative game, you have to play the role of a great magician who also has some grey shades. Do more aggressive and use all your skills to find a courageous volunteer, who gets mistakenly trapped into your wheel of death! You are the only person who can ensure him that everything is fine and you will him to come out of the danger. 

If you fail for a few moments, your audience is not going to leave you. Perform well to protect him and the volunteer against the blood-thirsty audience.
